Slave censuses
Rindeil cannot give shelter to a wanted man. However, if you steal the slave roster located next to the Portal during the Curse attack, it can make the tasks of Khadagan law enforcement officers more difficult.
#subobj 1
Get to the villa
Until the case is taken up by the investigating magistrates, the slave rosters are kept in the chief warden's mansion.
#subobj 2
Bypass the villa's security
The villa is well guarded, and you'd better not run into a guard.
#subobj 3
Steal the censuses
The slave censuses are on a table near the house.
#subobj 4
Free yourself from witnesses
The officials have noticed the theft! You need to get free from them.
